summary: This document certifies the incorporation of JEGE, INC. in New York and confirms that the corporation is currently existing with no records of dissolution found. It notes that the Biennial Statement is past due.

persons.name: Brendan W. Fitzgerald
persons.context: Brendan W. Fitzgerald is the official who certifies the incorporation of JEGE, INC. and provides the official seal of the Department of State.

events.title: Incorporation of JEGE, INC.
events.description: The Certificate of Incorporation for JEGE, INC. was filed.

events.title: Certification of Incorporation Status
events.description: Certification confirming that JEGE, INC. is an existing corporation and that the Biennial Statement is past due.

keyFacts: The Certificate of Incorporation for JEGE, INC. was filed on September 26, 2013.
The document certifies that JEGE, INC. is an existing corporation with no records of dissolution.
The Biennial Statement for JEGE, INC. is past due.
The certification was issued by Brendan W. Fitzgerald on August 10, 2017.
